Build Instructions for Escape The Robots And Oh Gosh They're Coming Run 2: The Better One

Requires Godot Engine 3.2.

1. Open Godot
2. Click "Scan"
3. Select the directory for the Escape The Robots And Oh Gosh They're Coming Run 2: The Better One
4. Double-click Escape The Robots And Oh Gosh They're Coming Run 2: The Better One
5. Click "Project" -> "Export"
6. Click "Add"
7. Choose your desired platform
8. Click the folder next to "Export Path"
9. Choose a path to export the binary to
10. Click "Export All"
